productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
one of my hobbies is poetry. and when i'm writing poems this works great.
